  "texts": [
    "RL has found practical application in environmental sustainability because the inherent uncertainty of this domain poses challenges to strategy learning and adaptation that can be naturally tackled by RL.",
    "The review of the literature performed in this survey has identified the most common applications of RL in environmental sustainability and the most popular methods used to address these challenges in the last two decades.",
    "We have first provided a quantitative analysis of the state-of-theart related to the application of RL in environmental sustainability and then analyzed the use of these techniques, focusing on sustainability concerns.",
    "In particular, we have provided an overview of the application domains of the proposed RL techniques and the approaches used for environmental sustainability issues.",
    "Moreover, we have narrowed our attention to 35 selected papers and provided technical information on the formalization of the RL problem, the performance measures adopted for evaluation, and the challenges addressed."
  ],
